Differentiation of energy
-----------------------------------
It is the sate of observation who observe the different state of energy and their intensity/capability. Observation not simply take the streaming of object in account but it observe the sate of energy transmit IN/OUT to the object and together the state of transformation during IN/OUT of energy. It thinning the IN/OUT energy as well as the state of transformation the object.
Distributing the the different sate within the a single sate is nothing but differentiation of states/states of energy, differentiation is one of the finding different states within
a state of energy, recognizing and picking up the different state of energy for further observation.

Ex-
When you have to know the flow of energy within tree, Every instance of tree are under flow of energy but you observation concentrate on IN/OUT ie the supply of energy form root,leaf and out the energy form flower/leaf/fruit and branch.Every instance of tree have different state of energy and their use. If you need wood then first you have to distinguish which part of tree provide wood. If you need sees then first you have to recognize which part of tree provide the sees, as it hide in fruit u need to know.

***Differentiation of energy is the purpose to know the different state of energy/it's intensity and their flow within object***

Integration of energy
-----------------------------
Integration of energy is nothing but summarization of different state of energy for use/observation, without knowing the importance the differentiation of state of energy you can,t integrate the same.

In differentiation your observation breaking the the state of energy within life/object as much possible/as much thing and when it get differentiate then finding the use/importance
of different state of energy and finally adding different state of energy to make the single as it is before differentiation.

Ex-
You body energy system can differentiate in different pat of energy system, your scenes is one energy system, your observation is another energy system, your senses is another
energy system, blood circulation is another energy system, your lust/love/feeling/understanding/realization/min/yours/..so are the different energy system within the body.

When you integrate these all(usual energy system) you get the body as live object, then you can understand a body is not simply look live live/active but there are billion of
energy system working together with body.

***Why not these energy system makes illusion when you look the activity of life as single energy system without differentiation of many energy system within it*** 
